{"id":195564,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/11/维权网-快讯：友人来访，上海维权人士冯正虎被/","date":"2011-11-11T19:00:47Z","modified":"2011-11-11T19:00:47Z","title":"维权网 | 快讯：友人来访，上海维权人士冯正虎被传唤","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\">      </a></span><span>（维权网信息员赵荣报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>点</span><span>，上海王扣玛、陈启勇、吴育青、陈国贵、张燕红、吴如云等访民到政通路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span><span>楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>号冯正虎家里去探望他，打算就法律维权的事向冯正虎咨询。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>正在大家畅谈之际，突然有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7~8</span><span>个自称是杨浦区的警察冲进冯正虎的家里，拿出一张很旧很皱的传唤证，说要传唤冯正虎，并让冯正虎在传唤证上签字，随后把冯正虎强制从家中带走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陈国贵在电话中说：我们几个和冯正虎是朋友，认识很久了。冯先生一直以来都帮助我们了解法律法规的相关知识，教我们如何用法律维护公民权益。我们听说他因为维护权益被软禁了，所以今天一起来看望他。没有想到看到这粗暴惊人的一幕。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155<span>  </span></span><span>陈启勇：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13585973365<span>  </span></span><span>吴育青：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13818408980<span>  </span></span><span>陈国贵：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13381884870</span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-3123943634031393678?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" width=\"1\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br /